data.message: Gabrielle I recommend Dinnaken if you're still looking for a place! I lived there my sophomore year and the staff is awesome. The rent is on the low end of that range. And I heard they are getting some updates! New floors and furniture is the rumor :)

message: Hello! Eryn Stewart and I are looking for one or two more roommates for next school year. We are looking at two bedroom apartments in the Stadium Village area that are within a reasonable price range (around $400-$550). If anyone is still looking for housing, please let me know!
